name: 'SYMBOL OF PERSISTENCE'
description:
When it comes to Patience, strength, and persistence there is only one inspiration in the world "women". The roles and responsibilities she has in life are different at different times which are shown in this Artwork by different shades and colors. 
 Gestures showed in this Artwork shows the pain and sufferings hid in women's life, which she faces up with confidence and gratitude.
This Artwork is an appreciation gesture to all the women on this planet. As a symbol of persistence, this artwork gives respect, pride, and support to all women.

'SYMBOL OF PERSISTENCE'
